{"tid":891011,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"Floyd Mayweather vs 日本視童那須川天心","createTime":"2018-11-05T19:08:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-01T00:49:51.000Z","uid":132262,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"613bc4b0c2951a92c5e8a99df1801054a78cb9d6","tid":891011,"uid":132262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T19:08:08.000Z","msg":"傳的沸沸揚揚的 Floyd vs Khabib 之戰還沒成真，今回 Floyd Mayweather 便為我們揭曉了其最新對手，那便是年僅 20 歲，被譽為「格鬥天才」的那須川天心（Tenshin Nasukawa）。那須川天心出道至今可說是戰功彪炳，16 歲成就 RISE 金腰帶、17 歳贏得ISKA -55kg 世界冠軍、18 歲 KO Lumpinee Boxing Stadium 王者，加上大大小小的戰績和業餘賽事經歷，在日本他儼然已是家喻戶曉的巨星。而此番雙方的約戰也將日期預定為 12 月 31 日於琦玉縣 Saitama Super Arena 進行，比賽形式還未確定是拳擊或著綜合格鬥。<br />\n<br />\n他此次的對手那須川天心，今年年僅20歲，卻有著日本格鬥神童之稱。在少年時已成名，並且被稱作最強高中生。這位20歲的小將16歲獲得3條世界級金腰帶，在17歲時還曾經參戰崑崙決東京站，1回合KO中國搏擊新星林斌。<br />\n<br />\n那須川天心是一個日本踢拳選手，曾因戰勝前IBF拳王阿泰倫龍，一戰成名，阿泰倫龍曾擊敗拳王鄒市明。目前那須川天心的戰績已經達到27-0，是個不敗神童。所以別看他年齡不大，但實際上，他的確是個高手。"},{"pid":"3648ac30862ccc675e4937075f1eef6f2cd6c2f0","tid":891011,"uid":132262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T07:21:06.000Z","msg":"可能打mma例"},{"pid":"3c5ccc7d35fcf65d96324b73a295e55d72bea832","tid":891011,"uid":154872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3648ac30862ccc675e4937075f1eef6f2cd6c2f0","tid":891011,"uid":132262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T07:21:06.000Z","msg":"可能打mma例"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T07:37:27.000Z","msg":"一定唔會, floyd個經理人先唔會咁蝕底"},{"pid":"0dcfb4a5e0e3050d6f3a8cdf01a70767d72d8f4d","tid":891011,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T08:08:39.000Z","msg":"侏儒大戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6284c384629fa5723bce0fe0bc7835f2cd2a557","tid":891011,"uid":8636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T08:35:39.000Z","msg":"Mayweather 幾時黎挑戰我地香港戰神 呀如"},{"pid":"3b131c9d5323339d0083fbce1184bea17022ab57","tid":891011,"uid":4525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f6284c384629fa5723bce0fe0bc7835f2cd2a557","tid":891011,"uid":8636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T08:35:39.000Z","msg":"Mayweather 幾時黎挑戰我地香港戰神 呀如"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T08:38:16.000Z","msg":"件老野邊夠膽<br />\n唔怕俾阿如打死咩"},{"pid":"81d701463bc8eade7964fb997f451bf7f4e27b6c","tid":891011,"uid":27265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T08:46:54.000Z","msg":"<strong>見到那須川Po上ig果時<br />\n以為係佢自己Key上去</strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"774d0e463282efd66a20afcbec2c80ea5f5cf4ee","tid":891011,"uid":9502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T02:45:15.000Z","msg":"Maychicken縮沙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b48b825bbc732a168a60108e64ccb8b22734f7f","tid":891011,"uid":194415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T03:16:30.000Z","msg":"Floyd Mayweather<br />\n龜縮拳擊"},{"pid":"446d55e3fcc63979a311d6fd50f38c8ba0b902c9","tid":891011,"uid":133424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T14:00:25.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"912678d84375c6cc46c4e895a539e082e637db33","tid":891011,"uid":74929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T00:49:51.000Z","msg":"秒殺"}]}